caption:
We are beyond thrilled to announce the newest member of the Bombay Brow family! Our co-founder, @ravymehroke delivered her third sweet angel, Iyla, August 20th. Mother and baby are doing fine and the rest of the family is feeling blessed to be surrounded by such outpouring of love.
.
“Iyla, we can’t wait to see who you will become and all the amazing things you will do,” said Ravy to her newborn 💕.
.
With a mom like Ravy, we imagine Iyla to be just as strong and gracious and wise. Congratulations to the Mehroke’s!
.
Big thank you as well to @sweet.little.delights for their beautiful and delicious surprise cake for baby Iyla! 😋 🎂.
.
